<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>

    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Contact - Cloth Shop</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Nunito', sans-serif;
            background-color: #F9F9F9;
            color: #333;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        header {
            background-color: #cedcd3;
            padding: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: white;
        }

        nav {
            background-color: #D7EAD9;
            padding: 10px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }

        nav a {
            margin: 0 15px;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #333;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: color 0.2s;
        }

        nav a:hover {
            color: #161817;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1000px;
            margin: 30px auto;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 2rem;
            color: #161817;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        p {
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .contact-info {
            background-color: #fff;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 25px;
            box-shadow: 0 3px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .contact-info h3 {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            color: #161817;
        }

        .contact-info p {
            margin: 5px 0;
        }

        form {
            background-color: #fff;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 25px;
            box-shadow: 0 3px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
        }

        form label {
            display: block;
            margin-top: 10px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #161817;
        }

        form input, form textarea {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 10px;
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin-top: 5px;
            font-family: inherit;
        }

        form button {
            margin-top: 20px;
            background-color: #D7EAD9;
            border: none;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background-color 0.2s;
        }

        form button:hover {
            background-color: #b8d6b9;
        }

        .map {
            margin-top: 30px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 3px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
        }

        footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: #999;
            margin-top: 40px;

        }

        @media(max-width: 600px) {
            .container {
                padding: 0 15px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="container">
    <h1>Contact Us</h1>
    <p>Weâ€™d love to hear from you! Whether you have a question about our products, orders, or partnerships, feel free to reach out to us using the details below or send us a message.</p>

    <div class="contact-info">

        <p><strong>Address:</strong> 123 Fashion Street, District 1, Ho Chi Minh City, Vietnam</p>
        <p><strong>Phone:</strong> +84 123 456 789</p>
        <p><strong>Email:</strong> support@clothshop.com</p>
        <p><strong>Working Hours:</strong> Mon - Sat: 9:00 AM - 8:00 PM</p>
    </div>

    <form>
        <h3 style="text-align:center;">Send Us a Message</h3>
        <label for="name">Your Name</label>
        <input type="text" id="name" placeholder="Enter your name" required>

        <label for="email">Your Email</label>
        <input type="email" id="email" placeholder="Enter your email" required>

        <label for="message">Message</label>
        <textarea id="message" rows="5" placeholder="Write your message here..." required></textarea>

        <button type="submit">Send Message</button>
    </form>


</div>

</body>
</html>
